<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhè me dà de jiù ēn, wǒ zěn néng hū lüè? zhè me dà de fú qì, wǒ yī dìng yào dé zhe.
 lái ba yé hé huá de zhòng bǎi xìng, wǒ men yī qǐ huān lè chàng gē.
 zàn měi tā de guó shì yǒng yuǎn de guó. tā de guó dù zhōng yǒu yī tiáo shēng mìng hé.
 lái ba, yī qiè gàn kě de rén kuài lái ba, bái bái de qǔ shuǐ hē.
 zhè me dà de jiù ēn, nǐ bù néng hū lüè. zhè me dà de fú qì, nǐ yī dìng yào dé zhe.
 lái ba xún qiú yé hé huá de rén, wǒ men yī qǐ qǔ shuǐ hē.</lyrics>
<title>zhè me dà de jiù ēn zěn néng hū lüè 迦南695</title>
<hymn_number>695</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>